Precedence Order (Which One Is Picked?) - inventry 
Order	Inventory Source	Priority
1Ô∏è‚É£	-i option in CLI	üî∫ Highest
2Ô∏è‚É£	inventory = ... in ansible.cfg	üîº Medium
3Ô∏è‚É£	Default /etc/ansible/hosts	üîΩ Lowest

